<li>Maintainer of several repositories for <a href="https://github.com/TerrashiftNET">@TerrashiftNET</a>
</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/tylerguy/Chat-Bubbles">Chat Bubbles </a>a react app that displays twitch chat messages using the twitch irc package, tmi.js</li>
</ul>
<em>Most of my ongoing projects are private, but this will likely change in the future once they are ready</em>      
      <Footer />
    </main>
